column5: Hi everyone, I'm Monique and I'm an OFNer.  For those who don't know me...ah never mind, you all know me   THIS IS VERY COOL!!
HI Monique,  Strange, I recall seeing a video of you and that is not what you said on the tape.
Welcome Monique, you'll probably like it around here.   No wait............ RUN, before its too late!!!!!  Joey
You can stay here for as long as you want but it will not be as exciting as living at home. I have seen the guy she sleeps with and ....well...... he wears a pink tutu.  Art
Hi Monique, keep that TJ guy in line will ya
LOL...welcome!!  Just watch out for a guy named TJ....oh, wait a minute.....
